---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Frequently asked questions"
description: "Practical VoiceTel FAQ covering accounts, pricing, voice, messaging, hosted PBX, emergency service, compatibility, and support."
---

<p class="eyebrow">Help</p>
<h1>Answers for buyers, developers, and telecom operators.</h1>
<p class="lede">The FAQ answers operational questions directly and routes readers to pricing, docs, or support when a detail depends on account configuration.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Contact support</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/docs/">Read docs</a>
</p>

{%- for cat in faqs.categories %}
<section id="{{ cat.id }}" class="section-block faq-block">
	<h2>{{ cat.label }}</h2>
	{%- for item in cat.items %}
	<details class="faq-item">
		<summary>{{ item.q }}</summary>
		{{ item.a | safe }}
	</details>
	{%- endfor %}
</section>
{%- endfor %}

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
	"@context": "https://schema.org",
	"@type": "FAQPage",
	"mainEntity": [
		{%- for item in faqs.flat %}
		{
			"@type": "Question",
			"name": {{ item.q | dump | safe }},
			"acceptedAnswer": {
				"@type": "Answer",
				"text": {{ (item.plain or item.a) | dump | safe }}
			}
		}{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
		{%- endfor %}
	]
}
</script>
